      <title>Immutable collections in Ruby with Hamster</title>
      <link>https://neiro.io/posts/2016-02-14-immutable-collections-in-ruby-with-hamster/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Feb 2016 10:00:00 +0100</pubDate>
